 <text>
  <front>
   <head>[In a triumphal car]</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1">
     <l n="1">— In a triumphal car,</l>
     <l n="2">Round the Town-house of Berwick,</l>
     <l n="3">The Genius of Tweed</l>
     <l n="4">Drove the Genius of Scotland,</l>
     <l n="5">From Berwick to town, on a mouthful of porter,</l>
     <l n="6">She begg'd at a door from a generous ostler.</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
  </body>
